Bus yehi khwahish hai ki mera har ek gaana aapka dost bane. 

Shuru se kiya tha shuru aaj dekho hum kahan aagaye, 
Jahan tak ka socha tha usse bhi aage, 
Kitni raatein jaage , khud ki kitni khushiyan kha gaye , 
Kheench hee lee naa success mehnaton ke baand dhaage. 

Wakt khud jhuka dekh ke mera sabar,
Tere dil ke cover pe ho photo meri naa ki forbes par, 
Ek khwahish or hai, 
Ki kabar pe meri likhna ye toh tha amar hai amar.
